description:
Danny recaps this week's Vanderpump Rules, which features a not-middle age Scheana YouTubing with Br*tt, plus J*x turning 40, and a blow-up between Tom and Katie. Then, special guest CT (Chris Tamburello) from MTV's The Challenge calls in to talk about the new season, the best players, spinoffs, and more!


CT Interview: 40:09ish
